<main id="buzz-content" class="main__content">
  <div class="article__content container">
    <div class="arttcle--show columns">
      <section class="more--content columns col-8 col-md-12">
        <h2 class="more-atricle--title col-12">最新文章</h2>
        <section class="more-atricle container col-12">
          <div class="columns">
            {{#each relatedArticle}}
            <div class="card card-container col-6 col-md-12">
              <div class="card-image">
                <a href="http://172.20.10.2:3000/articles/{{ this._id }}">
                  <amp-img
                    alt="view of the article content"
                    height="250"
                    layout="fixed-height"
                    src="{{ this.coverImage }}"
                  >
                  </amp-img>
                </a>
              </div>
              <a href="http://172.20.10.2:3000/articles/{{ this._id }}">
                <div class="card-header">
                  <div class="card-title h5">{{ this.title }}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                  {{ this.introduce }}
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
          </div>
        </section>
      </section>
      <section class="sidebar col-3 col-md-12" aria-label="Promoted content">
        <div id="#" class="introduce--website">
          <div class="introduce--description">
            <h2 class="introduce--header"><strong>關於解密之書</strong></h2>
            <amp-text class="introduce--content"
              >解密之書致力於「各國網站的生活技巧與終點整理」為主題，透過文字作品與圖文，濃縮並精簡內容，提供有趣且實用的重點筆記給你們。</amp-text
            >
          </div>
          <div class="introduce--link">
            <a class="et_pb_button et_pb_promo_button" href="#">閱讀更多</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
